1.due to excessive sweating in hand the answer (omr) and question paper get wet , to get rid out of this handkerchief is needed to dry hand from the sweat 
2.excessive sweating in feet leads slipping of feet from the slipper which will hurt the feet , so allow shoes to these studens 

I request the NTA(NEET UG 2025) to please allow the students who is suffering from hyperhidrosis to wear shoes and carry handkerchief.

I am hoping a reply from the agency (NTA-NEET UG 2025)  allowing students suffering from hyperhidrosis to wear shoes.
